1$1"},{"type":"Character","id":445},{"type":"Text","text":"看着周围昏迷的家族成员，拉维妮娅不禁一时失语。","id":446},{"type":"Text","text":"在这种情况下，德克萨斯居然还做到了留手，即使和家族打了这么久的交道，这依然有些超出了她的认知。","id":447},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#5$1","id":448},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"幸好你不是我的敌人。","id":449,"figure":"avg_4065_judge_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1","id":450},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"德克萨斯","text":"但是，看起来，我们也只能到此为止了。","id":451,"figure":"avg_1028_texas2_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#4$1","id":452},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"欸？","id":453,"figure":"avg_4065_judge_1#4$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":454},{"type":"Character","id":455},{"type":"StopMusic","fadetime":"2","id":456},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.7","id":457},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","id":458},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":459},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#4$1","id":460},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"莱昂？！","id":461,"figure":"avg_4065_judge_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","id":462},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"......拉维妮娅，你不该来的。","id":463,"figure":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$storyendjp_intro","key":"$storyendjp_loop","volume":"0.6","id":464,"musicid":2},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#8$1","id":465},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"有些话，我必须当面问贝纳尔多。","id":466,"figure":"avg_4065_judge_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","id":467},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"针对罗塞蒂家族领袖的刺杀已经决定了。","id":468,"figure":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"萨卢佐和贝洛内会联手。","id":469,"figure":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#6$1","id":470},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"这就是他的决定？","id":471,"figure":"avg_4065_judge_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1","id":472},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"这就是贝洛内的决定。","id":473,"figure":"avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#2$1","id":474},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"......","id":475,"figure":"avg_4065_judge_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_4065_judge_1#1$1","id":476},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"他在哪？","id":477,"figure":"avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1","id":478},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"宴会刚刚结束，父亲还在楼上。","id":479,"figure":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"莱昂图索","text":"你可以去见他，但什么都不会改变。","id":480,"figure":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":481},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":482},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.7","id":483},{"type":"Text","text":"一路上，拉维妮娅思考了千万种开口的方式。","id":484},{"type":"Text","text":"她有太多的问题想要质问贝纳尔多。","id":485},{"type":"Text","text":"她设想过无数种与贝纳尔多争吵的方式，以及结果。","id":486},{"type":"Text","text":"她以为自己足够愤怒。","id":487},{"type":"Text","text":"然而，当她踏入房间时，却被眼前的一幕震慑。","id":488},{"type":"Dialog","id":489},{"type":"Image","image":"33_i15","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","x":"150","y":"-50","fadetime":"0","id":490},{"type":"ImageTween","yTo":"70","duration":"45","block":"false","id":491},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":492},{"type":"Text","text":"贝纳尔多端坐在华贵的椅子上。","id":493},{"type":"Text","text":"他捧着一本装饰着荆棘的法典。","id":494},{"type":"Text","text":"与她手中的那本如出一辙。","id":495},{"type":"Text","text":"他低着头，手掌轻轻摩挲着法典，仿佛完全没有注意到——他的双手拂过尖刺，而鲜血缓缓流出。","id":496},{"type":"Text","text":"纷乱的思绪在此时凝固。","id":497},{"type":"Text","text":"最终，千言万语凝聚成了一句话——","id":498},{"type":"Dialog","id":499},{"type":"Image","image":"33_i15","xScale":"0.88","yScale":"0.88","x":"-50","y":"-25","fadetime":"1.5","id":500},{"type":"ImageTween","yTo":"25","duration":"30","block":"false","id":501},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":502},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"拉维妮娅","text":"为什么？","id":503,"figure":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":504},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":505},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"贝纳尔多","text":"游戏结束了，拉维妮娅。","id":506,"figure":"avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":507},{"type":"Image","image":"33_i15","xScale":"1.2","yScale":"1.2","x":"-180","y":"180","fadetime":"1.5","id":508},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":509},{"type":"Text","text":"只这一句，对于拉维妮娅来说，已经足够。","id":510},{"type":"Text","text":"仅仅是几秒钟的沉默，却耗尽了她所有的力气。","id":511},{"type":"Dialog","id":512},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.7","id":513},{"type":"Image","image":"33_i15","xScale":"1.2","yScale":"1.2","x":"150","y":"180","fadetime":"1","id":514},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":515},{"type":"ImageTween","xTo":"200","duration":"30","block":"false","id":516},{"type":"Text","text":"拉维妮娅转身离开，没有回头，生怕眼泪夺眶而出。","id":517},{"type":"Text","text":"贝纳尔多留在原地，不发一言，几颗血珠滴落地面。","id":518},{"type":"Dialog","id":519},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":520},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":521},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":522},{"type":"Image","id":523},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"a","fadetime":"1","id":524},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":525},{"type":"Character","id":526},{"type":"Image","id":527}],"characters":["贝纳尔多","莱昂图索","卢比奥","拉维妮娅","德克萨斯","萨卢佐家族成员","阿尔贝托","忠诚的家族成员","激进的家族成员"]}